                    <h1 style="font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 2.5rem; margin: 10px 0; color: #141312;">Loaded Lentil Stew Matrix</h1>
                    <p style="color: #555; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.1rem;">A masterclass in bulk legume hydration. By slowly simmering brown or green lentils with aromatic storage vegetables and a dash of acid, we generate an exceptionally filling, fiber-dense macro profile that requires only a single pot to deploy.</p>

                    <!-- Ingredient Breakdown Ledger -->
                    <h2 style="font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; margin-top: 40px; color: #141312;">1. Component Unit Ledger</h2>
                    <table class="audit-table">
